data.title: B Garage to B Site Aftershock
data.description: This is a good aftershock to kill or push your opponent out of B Site allowing you to push and take control.

data.title: A Main to Mid Vents Fault Line
data.description: This is a good fault line to assist your teammates in mid and allow them to get into mid vents.

data.title: B Garage to B Site Flashpoint
data.description: This is a good flashpoint for B Site that blind anyone playing close left or B Heaven.

data.title: A Main to A Rafter Aftershock
data.description: This aftershock allows you to get a kill on anyone playing in both A Rafter and under it.

data.title: A Main to A Site Flash
data.description: This flash allows you to blind the entire A site and A Rafter allowing your team to push in and take control of site.
